title Fluxo de MineraĂ§Ă£o e ConstruĂ§Ă£o de Grafos\n(GithubMiner + GitHub API + AdjacencyListGraph)

actor       "UsuĂ¡rio"          as User
participant "main.py"          as Main
participant "GithubMiner"      as Miner
participant "GitHub REST API"  as API
participant "AdjacencyListGraph\n(G1/G2/G3/Integrated)" as Graph

== InicializaĂ§Ă£o ==

User  -> Main   : executar main()
Main  -> Miner  : GithubMiner()
activate Miner
Miner -> Miner  : load_dotenv()\nlĂª GITHUB_TOKEN e GITHUB_REPOSITORY
Miner -> Main   : <<instĂ¢ncia criada>>
deactivate Miner

== Fase de MineraĂ§Ă£o: fetch_data(pages) ==

Main  -> Miner  : fetch_data(pages=3)
activate Miner

loop para cada pĂ¡gina em [1..pages]

    Miner -> API  : GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/issues\n?state=all&per_page=100&page={p}
    activate API
    API  --> Miner : lista de issues/PRs (JSON)
    deactivate API

    loop para cada item na lista

        Miner -> Miner : extrai author, detecta is_PR\nadiciona author a users_set

        ' â”€â”€ ComentĂ¡rios (sempre processados) â”€â”€
        Miner -> API  : GET {item.comments_url}
        activate API
        API  --> Miner : lista de comentĂ¡rios
        deactivate API

        loop para cada comentĂ¡rio
            alt commenter != author
                Miner -> Miner : edges_g1[(commenterâ†’author)] += 1\nedges_integrated[(commenterâ†’author)] += 2
                opt item NĂƒO Ă© PR (Issue)
                    Miner -> Miner : edges_integrated[(authorâ†’commenter)] += 3
                end
            else commenter == author
                Miner -> Miner : ignora auto-comentĂ¡rio
            end
        end

        alt item NĂƒO Ă© PR (Issue)

            alt state == "closed" AND closed_by != null
                Miner -> Miner : edges_g2[(closerâ†’author)] += 1
            end

        else item Ă‰ PR

            Miner -> API  : GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/{number}/reviews
            activate API
            API  --> Miner : lista de reviews
            deactivate API

            loop para cada review
                Miner -> Miner : edges_g3[(reviewerâ†’author)] += 1\nedges_integrated[(reviewerâ†’author)] += 4
            end

            Miner -> API  : GET /repos/{owner}/{repo}/pulls/{number}
            activate API
            API  --> Miner : detalhes do PR
            deactivate API

            alt merged == true AND merged_by != null
                Miner -> Miner : edges_g3[(mergerâ†’author)] += 1\nedges_integrated[(mergerâ†’author)] += 5
            end

        end

    end

end

Miner --> Main : <<dados acumulados>>
deactivate Miner

== Fase de ConstruĂ§Ă£o: build_graphs() ==

Main  -> Miner  : build_graphs()
activate Miner

Miner -> Miner  : ordena users_set alfabeticamente\ncria user_to_id e id_to_user

Miner -> Graph  : AdjacencyListGraph(numVertices) Ă— 4\n(G1, G2, G3, G_Integrated)
activate Graph
Graph --> Miner : instĂ¢ncias criadas
deactivate Graph

Miner -> Graph  : g.vertexLabels = [usernames...]
activate Graph
Graph --> Miner : labels definidas
deactivate Graph

loop para cada grafo e seus edges_dict
    loop para cada (u_name, v_name, weight)
        Miner -> Graph  : addEdge(u_id, v_id)
        Miner -> Graph  : setEdgeWeight(u_id, v_id, weight)
    end
end

Miner --> Main  : (g1, g2, g3, g_integrated)
deactivate Miner

== Fase de AnĂ¡lise ==

Main -> Main : GraphAnalytics(g_integrated)
Main -> Main : calcula mĂ©tricas e exibe resultados
Main -> Graph : exportToGEPHI("resultados/.../gephi.csv")

Main --> User : resultados exibidos + CSV gerado

